title: Ghoulboy Curse of dark sword. Action platformer
description: Ghoulboy: Curse of dark sword. Action platformer http://speed-imagens.net/imagens/66514ed412.jpg Ghoulboy: Curse of dark sword. Action platformer - take a brave guy through the dark dungeons and other gloomy locations inhabited by demons and monsters. The main hero of this Android game challenged the powers of evil. Now you must help the guy cope with demons, ghosts and other supernatural creatures. The hero is armed with a sword, a mace and throwing weapons. Use different weapons in the right moment to destroy monsters. Deactivate traps, interact with different objects, make the hero jump on the platforms. Gather trophies
